name: Stockholm 2021 – Pakke med legendelapper
description:
This pack contains a single Stockholm 2021 participant High Grade, or Gold embroidered patch.

50% of the proceeds from the sale of this pack support the included organizations.

Patches can be applied to any agent you own.
